The Durban metro police are urging people to stay away from Umhlanga Main beach. DURBAN - The Durban metro police are urging people to stay away from Umhlanga main beach. A humpback whale has washed up on shore. The animal was found in the surf near the Umhlanga lighthouse. WATCH: PE man nearly swallowed by a whale Authorities believe it's been dead for a few days. The whale will be disposed of by the relevant authorities. The beach has been closed to the public for now.